  * `chart-changed` - Fired when chart changes.

Attributes:

  * `start-angle` {`number`} - Donut angle where progress starts

  * `animated` {`boolean`} - Whether progress animates on first load

  * `complete` {`any[]`} - An array of completed values

  * `title` {`string`} - Title of donut

  * `image-src` {`string`} - Source of image in the center of the object.

  * `image-alt` {`string`} - Alt text for image.

  * `total` {`number`} - Array of incomplete values
